  <description type="morphology">Herbs, annual. Stems erect, mostly 0.3–1 m, glabrous. Leaves: petiole 1–3 cm; blade
        unlobed, variable, mostly lanceolate or ovate, 8–15 × 1–8 cm, base tapering, apex
        long-acuminate. Inflorescences variously fasciated, dense, crested or plumose. Flowers:
        tepals pink, red, yellow, purple, or white, faintly 3-veined at base, 5–8 mm, scarious;
        style elongate, 3–4 mm; stigmas 3. Utricles 3–4 mm. Seeds 6–10, 1.5 mm diam., faintly
        reticulate, shiny. 2n = 72.</description>
